Taller - Regresión Lineal

Author

Jean Pierre Enríquez

Carga de librerías

pacman::p_load(dplyr, tidyverse, openxlsx, GGally, ggplot2, VIM, mice)

Carga de datos

prices_ec <- read_csv("data/house_prices.csv")

prices_ec <- prices_ec %>% select(created_on, lat, lon, l1, l2, l3, l4, rooms,
                                  bedrooms, bathrooms, surface_total, surface_covered,
                                  price, currency, property_type, operation_type)                 

prices_reg <- prices_ec %>% select(rooms, bedrooms, bathrooms, surface_total, surface_covered,
                                  price, currency, operation_type) 

prices_reg <- prices_reg %>% filter(currency == "USD" & operation_type == "Venta" & price <= 10000000) %>% select(-currency, -operation_type)

Imputación de valores nulos

iter <- 10
imputed_data <- mice(prices_reg, m = iter, method = "pmm", seed = 123)
